===================================================================================
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 70
Content-Type: application/json
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)

{
    "code": "404", 
    "details": "E", 
    "reasonPhrase": "No context element found"
}


02. POST /v1/updateContext to create Entity E, attribute A
==========================================================
